Building vLitas

See doc/readme-qt.rst for instructions on building vLitas-Qt,
the intended-for-end-users, nice-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of vLitas.

See doc/build-*.txt for instructions on building vlitasd,
the intended-for-services, no-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of vLitas.

Further build information and documentation is available at
the official vLitas website, http://litas.github.io/vlitas
